data.title: Mrs Elizabeth Anna “Annie” Lavery Johnson ...
data.meta_description: Annie died of sleeping sickness while her husband George Dodo Johnson was overseas in WW2. She was a kindly, cheerful, person who died much too young. (George married Iris Simpson in 1947.) The photo was taken at the side of the family home at 380 Pacific Avenue in Winnipeg. Annie is on the right of the picture. Her...
